# Three.js Portfolio

This is a web-based portfolio showcasing the work and experiences of Flávia Iespa. The portfolio is built using HTML, JavaScript, and Three.js to create a 3D rotating globe and includes sections about Flávia's background, experiences, awards, skills, and contact information.

